item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Roland Grapow - Separate Ways (Worlds Apart) (Flac/Lossy)
item.description:
I'm looking for the Flac or the best quality file available of this cover by Roland Grapow.

"Separate Ways (Worlds Apart)" is a song by the band Journey, I'm looking the flac for the cover by Roland Grapow.

It was recorded during the sessions for the album "Kaleidoscope" (1999) and appears as a bonus track on the Japan edition of the album.

If someone gets it I would appreciate it, currently I only have an mp3 rip from YouTube that is of terrible quality and has saturated bass...
